sources.title: Highway Hell (1941) VINTAGE GRINDHOUSE
sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Presents Classic Movie Monday
Director: Patrick Carlyle
Highway Girls: Mary Chouning, Elizabeth Brady, Kay Young, Ruth Clardy & More!

 A bottom-feeding slimeball schemes to take over a roadside honky-tonk to use as a base for his stable of "Highway" gals. "Going my Way, Mister?"

ADDITIONAL MUSIC CREDIT
"Villainous Treachery" Composed by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
